If $q \in L_{1,1}$ then assumptions \eqref{eq8} - \eqref{eq11} are satisfied. Conversely, if assumptions \eqref{eq8} - \eqref{eq11} hold, then the scattering data $\mathcal{S}$, defined in \eqref{eq2}, corresponds to $q \in L_{1,1}$.
